# Review

Three checklists, used at different moments:

- **Per change** (always before commit/PR): `references/review-checklist.md` —
  scope, tests, docs sync, CI, temporary shims.
- **Architecture-impacting changes**: `references/architecture-review-checklist.md`
  — boundaries, ownership, concurrency, error handling, reversibility.
- **Periodic audit** (e.g. weekly): `references/agent-output-review-checklist.md`
  — the nine recurring agent failure modes across recent slices.

